text: Hello there! How is your labor day going?
Not, bad enjoying the day off. Yourself?
I am enjoying the day off as well
Seen any good movies lately?
I rewatched Deadpool 2. I always like to watch it at home and see what little things I missed in the theater. How about you
The last thing I saw at the Theater was antman and the wasp. I thought it was pretty good.
Oh it was? I did not know how that would be. I enjoy Paul Rudd though
I feel like it's a cleanser after infinity war, makes you laugh after infinity war scarred you for life. My girlfriend still hates Thanos.
lol well I am glad you liked it
So, going out for any barbecuing for the holiday today?
I am. I am headed over to my Dads later. How bout you
It's been storming pretty much all day toady, so we're staying inside.
Nothing wrong with that!
It has cooled everything down though, it's been quite hot for the past few days.
Good thing we have lots of ways to cool ourselves off
True that. I can't imagine how people lived before air conditioning.
Yeah. Especially being a kid in another country where basic needs are not met
Very true here I am complaining about the heat in Michigan of all places.
lol. Have you ever helped with a donation to non profits that help children in need
I once raised money for the Christian children's fund. I think they go by save the children now.
Oh that is a wonderful organization to donate to
